descriptionHTML:
=(^.^)=

Cats are starving! Hungry Cats is a sequel app of well known Nap Cats Watch Face, now bringing 7 new doodles from Saratelka.

Every moment is good for a snack. Don't miss any with this analog watch face!

7 hungry cats for 7 days of week. Enjoy this colorful analog watch with belly-worship-cats doodles by the illustrator Saratelka https://www.facebook.com/saratelka

Designed for Android Wear.
Supported smartwatches: LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Motorola Moto 360, Sony SmartWatch 3, Asus ZenWatch, Samsung Gear Live.

comments: OMG Why you do this to me!! I bought nap cats first, then I saw this one! I had to get it too. Best watch faces ever lol.
I love this watchface! Pity the cats are not actually "eating" the food. Also, the food animation is not working correctly if the "Rendering seconds" option is set to "tick".
Ahhhh! I love it! And napping one too! Thank you!
